      <h1 class="post-title">Portugal- A Justiça de Papel Apagado</h1>
      <p class="meta">Publicado em 2026-03-10 19:38:17</p>
      <figure class="post-thumb"><img src="https://fasgoncalves.github.io/fragmentoscaos-img/imagens/file_0000000060407243bf004f9454d6f162.jpg" alt=""></figure>
      <div class="post-content">
        <div style="background:#0b0b0b; color:#e8eef4; font-family:Georgia,serif; line-height:2.2; padding:10px; text-align:left;">

<div style="display:none;" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
